Message: My ads are gtting rejected, but ther are accurate

I'm sorry to hear that your ads are being rejected. There can be various reasons for ad rejection, such as incorrect conversion tracking setup or typographical errors. I recommend checking the email from Ad Support with the subject line ‘Urgent: Ad Rejected - Action Required’ to understand the specific reason for rejection. You can also review our advertising policy to ensure compliance before resubmitting your ads. If you believe the rejection was a misunderstanding, you can appeal by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com. For more details, please refer to this article: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next)
